SampleComment: DISASTER - Sonde batteries died in the field after temp at pH were recorded, no replacements were available. Extra routine bottle was filled at the site. Back at the lab,  sonde and cal cup were rinsed with tap water, and triple rinsed with DI water. The extra routine bottle was then added to cal cup and spc cond and DO readings were taken this way. As a result, DO readings are likely suspect. Windy; overcast; flow is likely the result of last week's snow fall.
